Package jde.util

Class Summary
AntServer AntServer.java provides an interface between the command line(or from Emacs) and the ant executable.
ClassInfo This class provides information about classes on jde-global-classpath.
CompileServer CompileServer.java provides an interface between the command line(or from Emacs) and the javac compiler.
Completion This class provides completion facilities.
DynamicClassLoader The class DynamicClassLoader extends the abstract class ClassLoader.

MultiValueMap A HashMap subclass which adds multiple values with the same key to a List of values.
